<p>Baby mama: Bachelor winner Anna Heinrich (pictured) announced in April that she is expecting her first with husband Tim Robards. And on Friday, she was enjoying a babymoon in Bryon Bay, showing off her blossoming bump in a bikini </p>

<p>She covered up with an open white shirt and wore sunglasses on her famous face, her hair worn in a loose ponytail. </p>

